I am no demon.

34
00:02:29,890 --> 00:02:32,540
Nor is Your Majesty a foolish emperor.

35
00:02:32,540 --> 00:02:36,960
I know you took the throne at a young age, unable to rule in person.

36
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:40,550
Many wished you harm, scheming for power.

37
00:02:41,710 --> 00:02:43,760
You only played the fool

38
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:48,190
to make your enemies drop their guard and keep your throne secure.

39
00:02:51,980 --> 00:02:54,360
How could you possibly know this?

40
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:57,240
All Your Majesty needs to know is this.

41
00:02:57,820 --> 00:03:03,270
No matter how many enemies surround you, I will always stand by your side.

42
00:03:09,940 --> 00:03:13,690
This is how you slipped
into my dreams, isn't it?

43
00:03:14,290 --> 00:03:15,890
Your dreams?

44
00:03:22,550 --> 00:03:24,880
Your Majesty has dreamed of me?

45
00:03:38,710 --> 00:03:42,530
Since you so want to know my purpose,

46
00:03:44,320 --> 00:03:46,850
then I shall tell you.

47
00:03:47,390 --> 00:03:51,430
We were once demon lovers,

48
00:03:52,150 --> 00:03:54,080
our fates bound across three lives.

49
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:56,110
But Your Majesty died too soon,

50
00:03:56,110 --> 00:04:01,750
so I had to come to the mortal realm to find you again.

51
00:04:04,770 --> 00:04:06,610
What kind of demon lovers?

52
00:04:08,890 --> 00:04:13,000
I was an otter,
and Your Majesty was a black serpent.

53
00:04:14,330 --> 00:04:15,980
Absurd.

54
00:04:16,610 --> 00:04:20,810
If it were true, show me your true form.

55
00:04:20,810 --> 00:04:24,680
It's late.
You still have morning court tomorrow.

56
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:27,180
You should rest now.

57
00:04:29,860 --> 00:04:33,400
No rush. We have all the time in the world.

58
00:04:49,370 --> 00:04:51,210
Keep your word.

59
00:04:55,460 --> 00:04:57,400
Our days together are just beginning.

60
00:04:58,610 --> 00:05:00,780
 Mother was right. 

61
00:05:00,780 --> 00:05:03,110
 Trust your own heart. 

62
00:05:37,370 --> 00:05:40,450
You two may go.

63
00:05:49,100 --> 00:05:51,450
I have matters to discuss.

64
00:05:51,450 --> 00:05:53,990
Please reveal yourself, Madam.

65
00:05:57,030 --> 00:06:00,350
So, you've received my little gift.

66
00:06:00,350 --> 00:06:04,230
Yes. News just came from the prison.

67
00:06:04,230 --> 00:06:07,520
Wei Xian Yu is dead.

68
00:06:08,490 --> 00:06:12,420
Then will you join hands with me?

69
00:06:12,420 --> 00:06:14,080
Of course.

70
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:19,760
I am willing to work with you, each of us getting what we need.

71
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:25,950
I've also heard that demon lady was wounded at the banquet.

72
00:06:25,950 --> 00:06:29,350
That must have been your doing.

73
00:06:29,350 --> 00:06:31,730
More than just wounded.

74
00:06:31,730 --> 00:06:35,810
I've planted a trace of my aura
in her demon core.

75
00:06:35,810 --> 00:06:38,900
It will flare up bit by bit.

76
00:06:38,900 --> 00:06:44,120
Fed by the grudges of humans,
her core will swell.

77
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:50,490
Once it's out of control,
she'll help us kill Sima Jiao.

78
00:07:06,340 --> 00:07:10,660
Your Majesty, this incense
soothes the mind eases pain,

79
00:07:10,660 --> 00:07:14,210
and relieves your headaches.

80
00:07:16,220 --> 00:07:18,460
How is Madam Yan?

81
00:07:18,460 --> 00:07:21,370
I changed her medicine today.

82
00:07:21,370 --> 00:07:26,500
But it seems Madam Yan
is using her own secret remedies.

83
00:07:28,490 --> 00:07:30,420
Let her do as she wishes.

84
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:36,980
Your Majesty, punish me.

85
00:07:37,790 --> 00:07:39,320
For what offense?

86
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:41,960
I told Marquis of Nanyan about Madam Yan,

87
00:07:41,960 --> 00:07:45,270
but failed to learn
what was planned at the banquet.

88
00:07:45,270 --> 00:07:47,390
That put Your Majesty in danger.

89
00:07:47,390 --> 00:07:51,650
Your Majesty bore no grudge, saved my parents, and even kept me in service.

90
00:07:51,650 --> 00:07:54,660
But I have been useless.

91
00:08:01,730 --> 00:08:03,730
I've told you many times.

92
00:08:03,730 --> 00:08:06,660
Your parents are my subjects.

93
00:08:06,660 --> 00:08:09,690
Saving them was no favor to you.

94
00:08:09,690 --> 00:08:13,830
He has not suspected you of anything.

95
00:08:13,830 --> 00:08:15,580
That proves you've done well.

96
00:08:15,580 --> 00:08:19,730
Just keep hiding your identity.

97
00:08:19,730 --> 00:08:23,620
Thank you for the great kindness.
I'll take my leave.

98
00:08:29,490 --> 00:08:33,060
Your Majesty, this was presented by Madam Yan.

99
00:08:46,610 --> 00:08:51,490
It's a record of Marquis of Nanyan pulling strings in Liyang.

100
00:08:51,490 --> 00:08:53,730
Why would she have it?

101
00:08:53,730 --> 00:08:58,730
By offering this to Your Majesty, Madam Yan is showing her loyalty.

102
00:09:00,460 --> 00:09:03,890
Your Majesty, Minister Chen seeks audience.

103
00:09:03,890 --> 00:09:05,490
Let him in.

104
00:09:08,300 --> 00:09:09,920
Your Majesty.

105
00:09:11,180 --> 00:09:12,970
Grave news!

106
00:09:13,900 --> 00:09:17,060
- What is it?
- The jailers say Wei Xian Yu is missing.

107
00:09:17,060 --> 00:09:20,280
He vanished into thin air.

108
00:09:25,890 --> 00:09:31,040
Declare to the world he has died in prison.

109
00:09:33,650 --> 00:09:36,300
So...

110
00:09:36,300 --> 00:09:39,980
that was Your Majesty's doing?

111
00:09:39,980 --> 00:09:43,980
Yet the jailers swear since last night there's been no disturbance.

112
00:09:43,980 --> 00:09:47,520
How did Your Majesty pull it off?

113
00:09:59,700 --> 00:10:02,320
Sima Jiao, what are you doing?

114
00:10:10,890 --> 00:10:16,030
You call his name in your dreams, yet wouldn't let him stay the night.

115
00:10:20,650 --> 00:10:24,150
It's thanks to you that Wei Xian Yu confessed about the Marquis.

116
00:10:24,750 --> 00:10:27,820
That account book in Sima Jiao's hands

117
00:10:27,820 --> 00:10:30,260
will surely aid him.

118
00:10:44,940 --> 00:10:47,820
 Thank you both for saving me. 

119
00:10:47,820 --> 00:10:51,440
 You escaped this time,
but beware of the Marquis' men. 

120
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:53,770
 Beware of him? 

121
00:10:53,770 --> 00:10:55,180
 What do you mean? 

122
00:10:55,180 --> 00:10:57,880
 Aren't you sent by the Marquis? 

123
00:10:59,860 --> 00:11:01,160
 Fool. 

124
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:02,710
 He meant to kill you. 

125
00:11:02,710 --> 00:11:05,930
 Without His Majesty and Madam Yan, you'd already be a corpse. 

126
00:11:05,930 --> 00:11:07,180
 No way. 

127
00:11:07,180 --> 00:11:08,820
 My family is still with him. 

128
00:11:08,820 --> 00:11:11,180
 He must know I could never betray him! 

129
00:11:11,180 --> 00:11:15,070
 Only the dead keep silent. 

130
00:11:17,990 --> 00:11:21,780
 Since he cast you aside, why would he spare your family? 

131
00:11:26,610 --> 00:11:31,100
 Marquis of Nanyan!
I swear I'll make you pay in blood! 

132
00:11:31,100 --> 00:11:36,560
 If you pledge to His Majesty, he'll help you avenge them. 

133
00:11:39,800 --> 00:11:41,540
 Rest easy. 

134
00:11:42,580 --> 00:11:48,040
 I'll tell His Majesty everything I know. 

135
00:11:48,040 --> 00:11:50,820
Had you not warned me
to save Wei Xian Yu first,

136
00:11:50,820 --> 00:11:55,010
he'd already be dead.

137
00:11:55,010 --> 00:11:57,410
What brings you here?

138
00:11:57,410 --> 00:11:59,460
Have you found You Yan?

139
00:11:59,460 --> 00:12:00,700
Yes.

140
00:12:00,700 --> 00:12:03,350
Nian Jiu followed Beauty Tong's demonic energy.

141
00:12:03,350 --> 00:12:05,340
Though he found no trace of You Yan,

142
00:12:05,340 --> 00:12:09,970
he did discover before her downfall, Beauty Tong had met with Marquis of Nanyan.

143
00:12:09,970 --> 00:12:11,970
The Marquis...

144
00:12:12,470 --> 00:12:15,490
He ordered Wei Xian Yu
to assassinate Sima Jiao.

145
00:12:15,490 --> 00:12:17,500
Was he colluding with You Yan?

146
00:12:17,500 --> 00:12:19,250
Highly possible.

147
00:12:19,250 --> 00:12:21,470
If the Marquis seizes the throne,

148
00:12:21,470 --> 00:12:25,980
then Sima Jiao will never achieve
whatever he seeks as emperor.

149
00:12:25,980 --> 00:12:27,860
Dream on!

150
00:12:27,860 --> 00:12:30,200
And I uncovered something crucial.

151
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:32,340
Hearing is false and seeing is true.

152
00:12:32,340 --> 00:12:34,360
Come with me.

153
00:12:49,030 --> 00:12:53,100
But... Madam Yan was just resting here.

154
00:12:56,370 --> 00:12:59,940
Jiang Cha, guard Ziquan Palace with them.
 

155
00:12:59,940 --> 00:13:02,410
Let no one know Madam Yan is absent.

156
00:13:02,410 --> 00:13:04,020
Yes.

157
