Chi An He and I searched
every corner of the Pavilion of Destiny.

158
00:13:09,800 --> 00:13:13,770
What the Hu Kingdom emperor
most fears You Yan coveting is the worship ritual.

159
00:13:13,770 --> 00:13:15,530
is the worship ritual.

160
00:13:15,530 --> 00:13:19,580
And this is the very site of that rite.

161
00:13:22,170 --> 00:13:24,660
&nbsp;

162
00:13:24,660 --> 00:13:28,280
A barrier woven of spiritual power
in the mortal realm?

163
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:33,530
Clearly this rite is a key part of Sima Jiao's plan here.

164
00:13:33,530 --> 00:13:36,740
He must know something we don't,

165
00:13:37,530 --> 00:13:40,280
and rushed to stop it.

166
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:43,770
Then You Yan aiding the Marquis

167
00:13:43,770 --> 00:13:46,590
must also be after this rite.

168
00:13:48,060 --> 00:13:50,430
We cannot let them succeed.

169
00:13:51,680 --> 00:13:54,370
&nbsp;

170
00:13:55,800 --> 00:13:58,670
Even the Spirit Fire can't break this barrier.

171
00:13:59,580 --> 00:14:01,180
There must be more to it.

172
00:14:01,180 --> 00:14:06,210
If I can enter,
I may learn Sima Jiao's true plan.

173
00:14:16,340 --> 00:14:21,700
If only Sima Jiao can regain his memory now, then all will be clear.

174
00:14:21,700 --> 00:14:23,460
But he has lost his memory, and we cannot break this barrier.

175
00:14:25,990 --> 00:14:29,400
Who knows what he and You Yan truly plot.
 

176
00:14:29,400 --> 00:14:31,820
Why make him remember?

177
00:14:31,820 --> 00:14:35,250
Better he just stay an emperor.

178
00:14:35,250 --> 00:14:39,260
Yet whatever he and You Yan seek is tied to that throne.

179
00:14:39,260 --> 00:14:42,730
So, I'll help him hold it steady.

180
00:14:42,730 --> 00:14:45,800
As for You Yan, he's a master of hiding.

181
00:14:45,800 --> 00:14:49,820
But we can use the Marquis
as bait to drag him out.

182
00:14:49,820 --> 00:14:52,410
Madam, one thing puzzles me.

183
00:14:52,410 --> 00:14:55,230
That demon lady just entered Sima Jiao's side.

184
00:14:55,230 --> 00:14:58,220
Why is she so blindly devoted to him?

185
00:14:58,220 --> 00:15:00,280
You may not know this.

186
00:15:00,280 --> 00:15:03,870
Sima Jiao and Liao Ting Yan were demon lovers in a past life.

187
00:15:03,870 --> 00:15:07,870
This life, they're fated to tangle again.

188
00:15:08,470 --> 00:15:10,680
If that's so,

189
00:15:10,680 --> 00:15:16,910
why not make use of it to our advantage?

190
00:15:18,920 --> 00:15:26,610
You mean to press Sima Jiao in court?

191
00:15:26,610 --> 00:15:31,300
An official proposed digging a canal

192
00:15:31,300 --> 00:15:33,220
between the Lan River and the Chi River.

193
00:15:33,220 --> 00:15:39,300
But the cost was far too great,
so I shelved it.

194
00:15:39,300 --> 00:15:44,010
If we hang this on Sima Jiao,

195
00:15:44,010 --> 00:15:48,580
and brand him a foolish tyrant,

196
00:15:48,580 --> 00:15:50,730
it will serve us well.

197
00:15:51,530 --> 00:15:55,300
But we'll need your help, Madam.

198
00:15:55,300 --> 00:15:57,450
Speak freely.

199
00:15:59,410 --> 00:16:02,680
I'll stir pressure in court,

200
00:16:02,680 --> 00:16:07,580
forcing Sima Jiao to order the canal.

201
00:16:07,580 --> 00:16:12,480
While it's being dug,
you need only create a disaster.

202
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:14,680
Excellent.

203
00:16:14,680 --> 00:16:17,010
The grudges of the people will fester,

204
00:16:17,010 --> 00:16:20,730
topple his throne,

205
00:16:20,730 --> 00:16:24,960
and swell Liao Ting Yan's demon core,

206
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:28,000
so she'll finish him for us.

207
00:16:34,460 --> 00:16:38,660
Marquis of Nanyan is really a master of deceit.

208
00:16:39,460 --> 00:16:41,130
Just now in court,

209
00:16:41,130 --> 00:16:44,060
he went on and on about building the canal.

210
00:16:44,700 --> 00:16:46,770
He put on such an earnest face

211
00:16:46,770 --> 00:16:48,460
that I almost believed

212
00:16:48,460 --> 00:16:51,130
he was a loyal minister serving the realm.

213
00:16:51,130 --> 00:16:56,040
I suspect he means
to trap Your Majesty in a dilemma.

214
00:16:58,130 --> 00:17:01,440
I grew up under his teaching.

215
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:06,350
There isn't a single trick of his I don't know.

216
00:17:07,890 --> 00:17:10,610
I'll wait and see

217
00:17:10,610 --> 00:17:12,610
what new tricks he dares try.

218
00:17:12,610 --> 00:17:14,550
Your Majesty stayed at Ziquan Palace all night,

219
00:17:14,550 --> 00:17:16,540
then faced court affairs at dawn.

220
00:17:16,540 --> 00:17:19,760
Perhaps you should rest.

221
00:17:20,510 --> 00:17:24,060
No, I'll stay at Ziquan Palace.

222
00:17:24,060 --> 00:17:26,930
Let's see when she'll return.

223
00:17:26,930 --> 00:17:28,820
You think I'm so easy to fool?

224
00:17:28,820 --> 00:17:30,540
Nothing but lies.

225
00:17:30,540 --> 00:17:34,210
If I came here myself,
I knew Madam Yan was inside.

226
00:17:34,210 --> 00:17:35,550
I dare not deceive.

227
00:17:35,550 --> 00:17:36,970
The madam truly isn't in the palace.

228
00:17:36,970 --> 00:17:39,180
- You...
- Stop.

229
00:17:42,580 --> 00:17:46,020
- Your Majesty.
- Si Xian, such temper.

230
00:17:46,020 --> 00:17:50,020
This must be Marquis of Nanyan's daughter.

231
00:17:50,020 --> 00:17:52,880
Here to pick faults with me?

232
00:17:52,880 --> 00:17:55,760
Your Majesty, I only thought
 

233
00:17:55,760 --> 00:17:57,260
Madam Yan is far from home

234
00:17:57,260 --> 00:17:59,060
and having just endured such misfortune,

235
00:17:59,060 --> 00:18:00,570
she must be unsettled.

236
00:18:00,570 --> 00:18:02,230
So, I came especially to visit her.

237
00:18:02,230 --> 00:18:04,060
But this maid kept...

238
00:18:04,060 --> 00:18:06,390
Still, no need to use force.

239
00:18:08,680 --> 00:18:10,350
Yes.

240
00:18:22,930 --> 00:18:25,480
Don't hurt yourself.

241
00:18:30,820 --> 00:18:34,040
Weren't you to dine with me tonight?

242
00:18:34,650 --> 00:18:37,070
 Yesterday, His Majesty refused me. 

243
00:18:37,070 --> 00:18:38,590
 Why the sudden change today? 

244
00:18:38,590 --> 00:18:40,690
Go prepare now.

245
00:18:42,020 --> 00:18:43,200
Understood.

246
00:18:43,200 --> 00:18:47,200
I'll return now to ready myself
for Your Majesty's visit.

247
00:18:48,030 --> 00:18:49,530
Let's go.

248
00:19:02,230 --> 00:19:04,050
Greetings to Your Majesty.

249
00:19:11,960 --> 00:19:14,310
I specially prepared this tea for you.

250
00:19:14,310 --> 00:19:16,140
It restores energy and calms the mind.

251
00:19:18,270 --> 00:19:20,010
Having a headache again?

252
00:19:23,710 --> 00:19:27,920
Dealing with Noble Consort Si Xian's father
in court by day,

253
00:19:27,920 --> 00:19:30,470
and coaxing her in the harem by night,

254
00:19:30,470 --> 00:19:33,660
how can you not have a headache?

255
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:37,940
And you weren't idle either.

256
00:19:39,270 --> 00:19:41,470
I came to Ziquan Palace

257
00:19:41,470 --> 00:19:43,940
and found you nowhere.

258
00:19:44,710 --> 00:19:46,250
Where were you?

259
