260
00:19:53,920 --> 00:19:57,140
I shouldn't have gone
to the Imperial Garden to practice.

261
00:19:58,230 --> 00:20:00,010
But I came last night.

262
00:20:05,120 --> 00:20:08,380
I couldn't sleep,

263
00:20:09,120 --> 00:20:12,790
so I wandered the Imperial Garden.

264
00:20:12,790 --> 00:20:14,490
And I got lost.

265
00:20:15,680 --> 00:20:18,920
Madam, His Majesty searched for you

266
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:21,940
many times in the garden alone.

267
00:20:25,030 --> 00:20:27,740
Well, I fell down a well. Do you believe me?

268
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:39,960
Deceiving the emperor is punishable by death.

269
00:20:39,960 --> 00:20:42,180
Choose your answer carefully, Madam.

270
00:20:44,600 --> 00:20:46,700
I don't wish to lie to Your Majesty.

271
00:20:47,640 --> 00:20:49,700
May I simply not speak?

272
00:21:06,160 --> 00:21:07,880
Have you thought of His Majesty?

273
00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:09,200
He worried over you so much.

274
00:21:09,200 --> 00:21:10,400
He waited here all night.

275
00:21:10,400 --> 00:21:11,990
He feared you might never return,

276
00:21:11,990 --> 00:21:14,270
feared Si Xian would seize on your absence.

277
00:21:14,270 --> 00:21:15,750
So, he kept it quiet,

278
00:21:15,750 --> 00:21:18,070
only sent men to search in secret.

279
00:21:18,070 --> 00:21:19,940
Why won't you tell me?

280
00:21:36,440 --> 00:21:40,960
If your head still aches,
let me massage it for you.

281
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:42,330
No need.

282
00:21:49,710 --> 00:21:52,070
I made Your Majesty wait all night.

283
00:21:52,070 --> 00:21:53,990
That was my fault.

284
00:21:53,990 --> 00:22:00,120
But I want you to know,
all I've done is for you,

285
00:22:00,120 --> 00:22:02,010
not for anyone else.

286
00:22:06,120 --> 00:22:08,420
I never doubted your heart.

287
00:22:09,840 --> 00:22:13,490
I only wish you can be more open.

288
00:22:20,950 --> 00:22:21,920
Forget it.

289
00:22:21,920 --> 00:22:27,510
Do you know why
I wept the first time I saw you?

290
00:22:27,510 --> 00:22:28,600
No.

291
00:22:28,600 --> 00:22:31,140
I've waited 19 years for you,

292
00:22:31,920 --> 00:22:34,570
fearing I'd never see you again.

293
00:22:35,360 --> 00:22:38,490
I have so much to say,

294
00:22:39,360 --> 00:22:41,250
so much to ask...

295
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:45,090
 Where have you been all these years? 

296
00:22:52,990 --> 00:22:54,990
 Sima Jiao? 

297
00:22:54,990 --> 00:22:56,850
 Sima Jiao! 

298
00:22:58,790 --> 00:23:01,070
Then why don't you ask?

299
00:23:01,070 --> 00:23:04,850
Seeing Your Majesty living well here now,

300
00:23:06,840 --> 00:23:08,380
that's enough for me.

301
00:23:14,120 --> 00:23:16,990
My headaches come from you.

302
00:23:16,990 --> 00:23:18,530
You must answer for them.

303
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:27,050
Physicians have tried for years

304
00:23:27,750 --> 00:23:30,330
and found no cure.

305
00:23:31,750 --> 00:23:33,400
Yet you can ease it.

306
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:35,290
Even now,

307
00:23:36,030 --> 00:23:37,680
you test me still.

308
00:23:37,680 --> 00:23:39,850
You always keep secrets from me,

309
00:23:40,680 --> 00:23:42,840
and won't let me wonder.

310
00:23:42,840 --> 00:23:44,750
So many worries.

311
00:23:45,440 --> 00:23:47,290
No wonder your head aches.

312
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:51,140
I am the emperor.

313
00:23:51,920 --> 00:23:54,310
How dare you be so bold with me.

314
00:23:54,310 --> 00:23:57,230
Even if you forbid it,

315
00:23:57,230 --> 00:23:59,700
I've been bold so many times.

316
00:24:02,270 --> 00:24:04,330
And you rather like it,

317
00:24:05,360 --> 00:24:06,770
don't you?

318
00:24:30,680 --> 00:24:32,710
At last, you smile.

319
00:24:32,710 --> 00:24:35,260
So, your mood is lighter.

320
00:24:40,790 --> 00:24:43,140
You wished only for my happiness.

321
00:24:44,990 --> 00:24:46,490
Yet, I...

322
00:24:47,840 --> 00:24:49,220
What is it?

323
00:24:50,680 --> 00:24:54,900
I shouldn't have used Si Xian to provoke you.

324
00:24:55,960 --> 00:25:00,530
Even without her, there are concubines aplenty.

325
00:25:03,120 --> 00:25:05,990
Behind each woman in the harem

326
00:25:05,990 --> 00:25:08,680
stands a faction with its schemes.

327
00:25:08,680 --> 00:25:10,570
Though I must balance them,

328
00:25:11,310 --> 00:25:14,140
I've never touched a single one.

329
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:20,360
But...

330
00:25:20,360 --> 00:25:22,250
you are different.

331
00:25:22,990 --> 00:25:25,140
What makes me different?

332
00:25:25,750 --> 00:25:29,880
You are the one who wants nothing from me,

333
00:25:29,880 --> 00:25:31,810
the one who visits me in dreams.

334
00:26:01,790 --> 00:26:03,790
Time for dinner.

335
00:26:03,790 --> 00:26:06,880
Won't you eat with Si Xian tonight?

336
00:26:06,880 --> 00:26:08,290
No.

337
00:26:09,160 --> 00:26:12,070
The Marquis forced me to build the canal.

338
00:26:12,070 --> 00:26:16,470
Let Si Xian take that as my reply.

339
00:26:16,470 --> 00:26:19,510
If the Marquis really colludes with You Yan,

340
00:26:19,510 --> 00:26:22,290
then this canal is far from simple.

341
00:26:23,030 --> 00:26:25,710
What's he scheming now?

342
00:26:25,710 --> 00:26:27,330
About the canal,

343
00:26:27,960 --> 00:26:31,070
if we build it, the people suffer.

344
00:26:31,070 --> 00:26:34,440
If we don't, transport suffers.

345
00:26:34,440 --> 00:26:36,510
The Marquis' pressuring me,

346
00:26:36,510 --> 00:26:40,400
hoping to trap me in a dilemma,
leaving me no way out.

347
00:26:40,400 --> 00:26:44,660
It does sound like there's no winning move.

348
00:26:46,230 --> 00:26:49,490
But Your Majesty looks calm,

349
00:26:50,270 --> 00:26:52,660
so you must already have a plan.

350
00:26:54,120 --> 00:27:00,680
I've ordered the canal
designed to suit the land,

351
00:27:00,680 --> 00:27:02,960
cutting costs by thirty percent.

352
00:27:02,960 --> 00:27:07,150
As for labor,
we'll pay fair wages to willing hands.

353
00:27:07,150 --> 00:27:11,260
It may take longer to finish the canal,

354
00:27:12,840 --> 00:27:14,510
but its benefits will last for ages.

355
00:27:14,510 --> 00:27:17,950
The canal is truly a blessing for the nation.

356
00:27:17,950 --> 00:27:21,230
Your Majesty should follow through,

357
00:27:21,230 --> 00:27:23,510
perhaps even gain more than expected.

358
00:27:23,510 --> 00:27:25,710
You are Heaven's chosen.

359
00:27:25,710 --> 00:27:27,380
Heaven itself will aid you.

360
00:27:30,750 --> 00:27:36,920
Demon lady, your sweet talk
only clouds my mind.

361
00:27:36,920 --> 00:27:41,400
I told you, I'm a fairy.

362
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:44,080
Even if you want stars from the sky,

363
00:27:44,080 --> 00:27:46,490
I'll pluck them down for you.

364
00:27:56,230 --> 00:27:58,450
I don't want stars.

365
00:27:59,230 --> 00:28:01,670
I only want a clear and steady court.

366
00:28:01,670 --> 00:28:03,560
That alone will satisfy me.

367
00:28:03,560 --> 00:28:05,290
If possible,

368
00:28:06,880 --> 00:28:09,510
I'd rather be an ordinary man,

369
00:28:09,510 --> 00:28:11,850
enjoy life's simple pleasures,

370
00:28:12,470 --> 00:28:14,180
carefree and free.

371
00:28:17,080 --> 00:28:18,600
 Here, My Lord. 

372
00:28:18,600 --> 00:28:19,940
 Smells nice! 

373
00:28:29,290 --> 00:28:33,230
Still, I've known since birth

374
00:28:33,230 --> 00:28:35,880
that I bear the weight of Hu Kingdom.

375
00:28:35,880 --> 00:28:38,400
All I wish is to keep this land safe.

376
00:28:38,400 --> 00:28:43,190
Then let me see to your peace and comfort.

377
00:28:43,190 --> 00:28:45,640
So, you may have both.

378
00:28:45,640 --> 00:28:49,450
The warmth of everyday life and the throne.

379
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:58,470
Grand Preceptor, can't you see further?

380
00:28:58,470 --> 00:29:02,080
The canal will divert the Lan River,

381
00:29:02,080 --> 00:29:07,710
stop the yearly floods,
open the north-south waterway,

382
00:29:07,710 --> 00:29:10,030
and bring wealth to the counties along it.

383
00:29:10,030 --> 00:29:14,030
It will bless future generations!

384
00:29:14,030 --> 00:29:15,560
Future generations?

385
00:29:15,560 --> 00:29:18,120
Shouldn't you look to the present?

386
00:29:18,120 --> 00:29:21,320
Since the late emperor's passing,
Yan Prefecture has suffered drought.

387
00:29:21,320 --> 00:29:25,270
Countless go hungry, families ruined,

388
00:29:25,270 --> 00:29:28,670
even children eaten by parents!

389
00:29:28,670 --> 00:29:30,670
And now you want a canal?

390
00:29:30,670 --> 00:29:32,750
Such a massive operation!

391
00:29:32,750 --> 00:29:36,920
How many laborers will be dragged into it?

392
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:38,840
And so what?

393
00:29:38,840 --> 00:29:41,800
Some sacrifice for glory lasting millennia.

394
00:29:41,800 --> 00:29:43,030
Which weighs more?

395
00:29:43,030 --> 00:29:45,950
My Lord, you are wrong!

396
00:29:45,950 --> 00:29:47,400
The people are the foundation.

397
00:29:47,400 --> 00:29:48,880
A strong foundation makes a stable state.

398
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:54,560
Draining the people will enrage Heaven and man!

399
00:29:54,560 --> 00:29:59,510
When the people rebel, what legacy remains?

400
00:29:59,510 --> 00:30:01,080
Enough, Grand Preceptor.

401
00:30:01,080 --> 00:30:05,750
You've grown too old,
confusing right and wrong.

402
00:30:05,750 --> 00:30:08,400
Better retire to your hometown.

403
00:30:08,400 --> 00:30:09,840
Hey!

404
00:30:09,840 --> 00:30:13,430
Your Majesty,
the canal has been debated for days.

405
00:30:13,430 --> 00:30:15,510
Please, give a ruling.

406
00:30:15,510 --> 00:30:23,940
Your words show such devotion to the people,
such tireless concern.

407
00:30:25,120 --> 00:30:30,510
Sharing Your Majesty's burdens,
toiling for the people, that is my duty.

408
00:30:30,510 --> 00:30:35,180
For this, I will give my all
and serve until death.

409
00:30:36,470 --> 00:30:41,860
Uncle, your diligence puts me to shame.

410
00:30:42,750 --> 00:30:47,250
Why not just take my throne yourself?

411
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:57,400
Your Majesty is now the ruler of a nation.

412
00:30:57,400 --> 00:31:01,340
How can you still joke like this?

413
00:31:02,320 --> 00:31:04,580
Without the worship ritual,

414
00:31:05,230 --> 00:31:07,450
how can I call myself emperor?

415
00:31:08,360 --> 00:31:11,210
Please, mind your words.

416
00:31:15,710 --> 00:31:18,340
No need to take it so seriously, Uncle.

417
00:31:20,080 --> 00:31:21,430
All right.

418
00:31:21,430 --> 00:31:24,360
Since the Marquis insists,

419
00:31:24,360 --> 00:31:25,940
then let it be built.

420
00:31:32,920 --> 00:31:35,450
See Your Majesty off.

421
00:31:45,230 --> 00:31:47,270
Send Chi An He and two demon generals

422
00:31:47,270 --> 00:31:49,380
to help Sima Jiao with the canal.

423
00:31:50,920 --> 00:31:54,360
You'll use the power
of the Immortal-Demon Ruler

424
00:31:54,360 --> 00:31:58,120
to aid a mere mortal emperor?

425
00:31:58,120 --> 00:32:00,230
He's not just any emperor.

426
00:32:00,230 --> 00:32:02,290
He's my sweetie.

427
00:32:03,160 --> 00:32:04,660
Fine.

428
00:32:05,640 --> 00:32:09,560
But seriously, what is your true aim?

429
00:32:09,560 --> 00:32:11,080
Sima Jiao told me

430
00:32:11,080 --> 00:32:14,030
Marquis of Nanyan is pushing hard on the canal.

431
00:32:14,030 --> 00:32:17,080
It must be a scheme
he and You Yan have plotted.

432
00:32:17,080 --> 00:32:19,880
Then let's play along,
see what they're plotting.

433
00:32:19,880 --> 00:32:22,770
We might even draw You Yan out.

434
00:32:33,560 --> 00:32:35,230
Avoid farmland and villages.

435
00:32:35,230 --> 00:32:36,800
That was Her Majesty's order.

436
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:38,180
Understood.

437
00:32:56,600 --> 00:32:58,800
Wh-What's happening?

438
00:32:58,800 --> 00:33:00,670
This flash flood is strange.

439
00:33:00,670 --> 00:33:03,450
Why would it cross high ground
to hit the village?

440
00:33:10,190 --> 00:33:11,240
It must be You Yan's doing.

441
00:33:11,240 --> 00:33:14,190
Ting Yan cautioned us,
the villagers' safety comes first.

442
00:33:14,190 --> 00:33:15,560
I'll go after him.

443
00:33:15,560 --> 00:33:17,320
You guys stay here and guard the people.

444
00:33:17,320 --> 00:33:18,530
Yes, sir.

445
00:33:30,840 --> 00:33:33,210
 This useless body... 

446
00:33:35,120 --> 00:33:37,010
 He caught up so fast! 

447
00:33:42,920 --> 00:33:47,010
Oh no, he got away.

448
00:33:57,560 --> 00:33:59,950
Nian Jiu, did you find You Yan?

449
00:33:59,950 --> 00:34:01,320
He escaped.

450
00:34:01,320 --> 00:34:02,670
Ting Yan was right.

451
00:34:02,670 --> 00:34:06,160
The canal project is no doubt
a trap set by You Yan.

452
00:34:06,160 --> 00:34:07,160
No wonder.

453
00:34:07,160 --> 00:34:08,840
An He and I were working.

454
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:10,240
Everything went smoothly.

455
00:34:10,240 --> 00:34:12,110
But just as we neared completion,

456
00:34:12,110 --> 00:34:14,800
the dike was destroyed,
and the flood burst out.

457
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:17,890
We nearly lost it all.

458
00:34:37,630 --> 00:34:39,500
Madam...

459
00:34:45,430 --> 00:34:46,510
Liang Chen.

460
00:34:46,510 --> 00:34:48,360
I'm sorry.

461
00:34:48,360 --> 00:34:50,030
Are you hurt?

462
00:34:50,030 --> 00:34:51,240
I'm fine.

463
00:34:51,240 --> 00:34:54,210
Madam, were you having a nightmare?

464
00:34:55,990 --> 00:35:02,430
 It seems... the demonic energy
You Yan left in me has begun to stir. 

465
00:35:02,430 --> 00:35:04,880
Your Majesty, urgent reports have arrived
from every province.

466
00:35:04,880 --> 00:35:07,180
The canal was finished overnight!

467
00:35:08,510 --> 00:35:09,550
Overnight?

468
00:35:09,550 --> 00:35:10,680
Yes.

469
00:35:10,680 --> 00:35:12,280
Villagers saw divine figures

470
00:35:12,280 --> 00:35:14,030
guiding the flood into the channel.

471
00:35:14,030 --> 00:35:16,920
And at once the canal was formed.

472
00:35:16,920 --> 00:35:20,770
The officials' reports
even included drawings of it.

473
00:35:29,880 --> 00:35:31,360
Now the people believe

474
00:35:31,360 --> 00:35:34,150
it's due to Your Majesty's blessing,

475
00:35:34,150 --> 00:35:35,890
a great fortune for all.

476
00:35:37,720 --> 00:35:41,150
 I told you, I'm a fairy. 

477
00:35:41,150 --> 00:35:43,430
 Even if you want stars from the sky, 

478
00:35:43,430 --> 00:35:45,890
 I'll pluck them down for you. 

479
00:35:46,590 --> 00:35:48,770
She really did pluck a star for me.

480
00:36:07,990 --> 00:36:10,660
At least hide yourselves better next time.

481
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:15,370
Got it.

482
00:36:15,990 --> 00:36:17,410
Grandmaster...

483
00:36:18,920 --> 00:36:20,810
He's not dead.

484
00:36:24,280 --> 00:36:25,920
Really, you guys.

485
00:36:25,920 --> 00:36:28,150
Why barge into the palace?

486
00:36:28,150 --> 00:36:31,280
I finally got Sima Jiao to trust me,

487
00:36:31,280 --> 00:36:33,540
and now he'll start doubting again.

488
00:36:34,950 --> 00:36:38,240
Your Majesty, when we were
working on the canal,

489
00:36:38,240 --> 00:36:39,730
a sudden flood struck.

490
00:36:40,470 --> 00:36:43,030
It was indeed You Yan's doing.

491
00:36:43,030 --> 00:36:45,760
He possessed Bi An's body.

492
00:36:45,760 --> 00:36:49,930
But... but I failed to catch him.

493
00:36:50,840 --> 00:36:52,720
He escaped again.

494
00:36:52,720 --> 00:36:54,880
We'll need another way to trap him.

495
00:36:54,880 --> 00:36:56,580
Don't worry, Your Majesty.

496
00:36:57,320 --> 00:36:59,320
Once Grandmaster regains his memory,

497
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:01,280
perhaps we'll know his plan.

498
00:37:01,280 --> 00:37:02,810
That'll be too late.

499
00:37:03,680 --> 00:37:05,990
Sima Jiao hides things from us all.

500
00:37:05,990 --> 00:37:08,290
This must be deadly serious.

501
00:37:08,920 --> 00:37:11,540
I must learn his plan soon.

502
00:37:13,200 --> 00:37:15,840
Next time, send word to me first.

503
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:17,510
Don't barge into my chambers.

504
00:37:17,510 --> 00:37:20,630
I... I just missed Grandmaster.

505
00:37:20,630 --> 00:37:22,030
And you didn't miss me?

506
00:37:22,030 --> 00:37:23,550
Of course I did!

507
00:37:23,550 --> 00:37:25,660
If I didn't,

508
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:30,760
why would I bring your favorite Spirit Dew?

509
00:37:30,760 --> 00:37:32,620
Thoughtful of you!

510
00:38:06,800 --> 00:38:08,290
Earlier...

511
00:38:09,030 --> 00:38:10,920
was someone else here?

512
00:38:10,920 --> 00:38:12,470
No, no one.

513
00:38:12,470 --> 00:38:14,290
You must've dreamed it.

514
00:38:42,200 --> 00:38:43,730
 Sima Jiao! 

515
00:39:11,990 --> 00:39:13,370
 Is it because 

516
00:39:14,510 --> 00:39:17,110
 of that past-life bond she spoke of, 

517
00:39:17,110 --> 00:39:19,770
 that I feel so at peace beside her? 

518
00:39:23,680 --> 00:39:25,210
 But maybe, 

519
00:39:26,840 --> 00:39:28,460
 at her side, 

520
00:39:30,510 --> 00:39:32,980
 there are things I don't know. 

521
00:39:35,110 --> 00:39:36,920
You must've all heard

522
00:39:36,920 --> 00:39:40,290
the tale of the canal forming overnight.

523
00:39:40,990 --> 00:39:45,060
Marquis, what say you?

524
00:39:47,320 --> 00:39:50,840
Surely it was Your Majesty's blessing.

525
00:39:50,840 --> 00:39:52,800
A fortune for the people.

526
00:39:52,800 --> 00:39:54,150
And the rest of you?

527
00:39:54,150 --> 00:40:00,470
It must be Your Majesty's blessing,
a fortune for the people!

528
00:40:00,470 --> 00:40:02,110
Good.

529
00:40:02,110 --> 00:40:04,580
Then we are agreed.

530
00:40:05,240 --> 00:40:09,630
But speaking of blessings,
since Madam Yan came to me,

531
00:40:09,630 --> 00:40:12,320
everything has gone my way.

532
00:40:12,320 --> 00:40:14,550
Even this canal's success

533
00:40:14,550 --> 00:40:16,430
seems owed to her.

534
00:40:16,430 --> 00:40:17,880
Indeed.

535
00:40:17,880 --> 00:40:19,630
All thanks to Madam Yan.

536
